 When we rode on the merry-go-round
I kissed Louisa 

1047
01:13:57,760 --> 01:14:01,673
 And then Louisa
Louisa kissed me 

1048
01:14:02,200 --> 01:14:06,478
 We were so happy
So happy and free 

1049
01:14:06,760 --> 01:14:10,958
 Ach! Ach! But she's a
beautiful Louisa 

1050
01:14:11,040 --> 01:14:15,397
 Ach! When I choose 'em
I never want to lose 'em 

1051
