1371
01:45:23,040 --> 01:45:25,110
Tony, the whole company got together.

1372
01:45:25,200 --> 01:45:28,317
We all chipped in,
and we bought you... nothing.

1373
01:45:29,080 --> 01:45:30,832
So we have nothing to give you...

1374
01:45:30,920 --> 01:45:34,037
but our gratitude, our admiration...

1375
01:45:34,800 --> 01:45:36,518
and our love.

1376
01:45:36,840 --> 01:45:38,717
The show's a hit, but we all feel...

1377
01:45:38,800 --> 01:45:42,679
no matter what might've happened to it,
it was wonderful knowing you...

1378
01:45:43,840 --> 01:45:45,398
working with you.

1379
01:45:45,680 --> 01:45:48,877
Maybe some of us didn't see eye to eye
with you at the beginning.

1380
01:45:48,960 --> 01:45:51,599
Maybe we thought
we wouldn't work out together...

1381
01:45:52,240 --> 01:45:53,559
but we have.

1382
01:45:54,480 --> 01:45:56,948
Yes, there were obstacles between us...

1383
01:45:58,720 --> 01:46:00,915
but we've kissed them good-bye.

1384
01:46:02,080 --> 01:46:06,198
We've come to love you, Tony.
We belong together.

1385
01:46:08,000 --> 01:46:10,116
The show's going to run a long time.

1386
01:46:11,160 --> 01:46:15,119
As far as I'm concerned,
it's going to run forever.

1387
01:46:24,600 --> 01:46:27,319
- Tony.
- May we say something?

1388
01:46:27,800 --> 01:46:30,837
 A show that is really a show 

1389
01:46:30,920 --> 01:46:34,356
 Sends you out with a kind of a glow 

1390
01:46:34,440 --> 01:46:38,069
 And you say as you go on your way 

1391
01:46:39,160 --> 01:46:41,628
 '"That's Entertainment! '" 

1392
01:46:42,440 --> 01:46:45,159
 A song that is winging along 

1393
01:46:45,240 --> 01:46:48,755
 or a dance with a touch of romance 

1394
01:46:48,840 --> 01:46:52,310
 is the art that appeals to the heart 

1395
01:46:53,480 --> 01:46:56,278
 That's Entertainment! 

1396
